nit, there is a IsEmptyCollection.empty() matcher, often used with the is matcher:
assertThat(offensiveStandard.getNames(), is(empty());

Have you considered using the matcher? If the test fails that matcher will print the contents of the collection rather than reporting simply that the size was not zero.

